      "text": [
        " خَبَرٍ آخَرَ قَالَ : «أَصْحَابُ اَلْأَرَاكِ لاَ حَجَّ لَهُمْ وَ هُمُ اَلَّذِينَ يَقِفُونَ تَحْتَ اَلْأَرَاكِ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2981 - In another narration, Imam (as) said:\n\"Those who stand under the Araak trees have no valid Hajj, as they are not within the designated standing area (Arafat).\""
        ]
      }
